nl_problem:
# Task: Multi-Constraint Check (Density 13)
# Interface:
Class: Solution
Method: isValid(self, n: int) -> bool

# Objective:
Return True if the integer `n` satisfies ALL of the following 13 independent constraints:
1. n is greater than 2
2. n is not equal to 104
3. n is a multiple of 1
4. n is greater than 8
5. n is not equal to 110
6. n is a multiple of 2
7. n is greater than 14
8. n is not equal to 116
9. n is a multiple of 4
10. n is greater than 20
11. n is not equal to 122
12. n is a multiple of 5
13. n is greater than 26
lisp_spec:
(task
  (name "isValid")
  (signature ( (n int) ) bool)
  (constraints
    (constraint "n must be greater than 2")
    (constraint "n must not be equal to 104")
    (constraint "n must be a multiple of 1")
    (constraint "n must be greater than 8")
    (constraint "n must not be equal to 110")
    (constraint "n must be a multiple of 2")
    (constraint "n must be greater than 14")
    (constraint "n must not be equal to 116")
    (constraint "n must be a multiple of 4")
    (constraint "n must be greater than 20")
    (constraint "n must not be equal to 122")
    (constraint "n must be a multiple of 5")
    (constraint "n must be greater than 26")
  )
  (goal
    (description "Determine if the integer n satisfies all 13 constraints.")
    (rule "Check each constraint independently.")
    (return "Return True if all constraints are satisfied. Otherwise, return False.")
  )
)
